Subject: Killfest and Speedbreaker weapons unload
From: Jeremiah <rdahl@...>

Speedbreaker couldnt wait any longer for Killfest to recover from his ride
and get off, there where Maximals to slag. He transformed, probably sending
Killfest to the ground, "Sorry buddy" he said friendly, "But I got some
Maximals to Break Down" he finished cruely, as he aimed upwards, and fired
his Break Down gun once at Angel Prime and once at Epyon. They probably
wouldnt even realize he was there till it was too late.
